  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "蒋蒋蒋蒋~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "女王登场！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "欢呼~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "掌声~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "在哪里呀？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771871633185202733.webp]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "欢呼。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "掌声。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "在这里。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "噗。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "林教授，你这个回答也太有意思了吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "没想到你居然会这么配合我。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还以为你会是那种高冷的，学术型的，不喜欢开玩笑的那种。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是这几天哪里做的不好，居然给你留下了这种印象？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你别看我这个样子，其实我也算是一个社牛的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "一社交就像牛一样沉闷的社牛？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，真是一个社牛的新解释啊。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我从来都不知道社牛还能这么解释。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "厉害，不愧是你。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "嘻嘻~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你别看我这个样子，强词夺理可是我最擅长的啦！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "今天找我是有什么事情吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "呜呜呜~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "男人的嘴，骗人的鬼。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "昨天还小甜心，小宝贝的叫着，今天就开始嫌弃起来了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "还问我有没有事。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么啦！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "没事就不能找你了吗？！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "哼，过分。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "臭男人。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没有。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是什么男人的嘴，骗人的鬼。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也没有喊过你什么甜心和宝贝。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "现在不就喊了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "来，再喊两声。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "爷给你打赏！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "【砰砰砰，甩下两个金子。】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": ".......",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢爷的打赏。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "打赏的收了，声音呢？我咋没有听见呀？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "虚无的金子，只能得到虚无的喊声。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "将就着听听吧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "唔...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "好啦，我听见啦！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "声音超级甜，是甜美的声音，爷我喜欢，再打赏你十个金子！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢爷的打赏。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "小的还要备课，就先退下了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "退下吧，小林子！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    }
